data.name: AllowRegistration.HelpText
data.value: Ngaba ufuna ukuba iindwendwe ezingaziwa zikwazi ukubhalisa i-akhawunti kwi-site

data.name: ProfileUrl.HelpText
data.value: Ngokukhetha ukubonelela nge-URL yenkangeleko yomsebenzisi esenzelwe yona

data.name: LockoutDuration.HelpText
data.value: Inani lemizuzu umsebenzisi kufuneka atshixwe ngaphandle

data.name: MaximumFailures.HelpText
data.value: Elona nani liphezulu leenzame zokungena ngaphambi kokuba umsebenzisi atshixelwe ngaphandle

data.name: RequireDigit.HelpText
data.value: Bonisa ukuba i-password kufuneka iqulathe umvo

data.name: RequireLower.HelpText
data.value: Bonisa ukuba i-password kufuneka iqulathe uphawu oluncinci na

data.name: RequirePunctuation.HelpText
data.value: Bonisa ukuba i-password imele iqulathe uphawu olungeyi-alphanumeric (o.k.t. iziphumlisi zeziphumlisi)

data.name: RequireUpper.HelpText
data.value: Bonisa ukuba ii-password kufuneka ziqulathe oonombumba abancinci na

data.name: Success.UpdateConfig.Restart
data.value: Uqwalaselo luhlaziyiwe. Nceda ukhethe ukuqala kwakhona inkqubo ukuze olu tshintsho lusebenze.

data.name: UniqueCharacters.HelpText
data.value: Elona nani lincinci leempawu ezikhethekileyo ekufuneka ziqulethwe yi-password

data.name: AllowSiteLogin.HelpText
data.value: Ingaba uyafuna ukuvumela abasebenzisi ukuba bangene besebenzisa igama lomsebenzisi kunye negama lokugqitha elilawulwa ekuhlaleni kule ndawo? Qaphela ukuba kufuneka ukhubaze olu khetho kuphela ukuba sele uqwalasele ngempumelelo umnikezeli wokungena wangaphandle, kungenjalo ungazitshixa ngaphandle kwesiza.

data.name: Authority.HelpText
data.value: I-URL yegunya okanye i-URL yomkhupheli enxulunyaniswa nomnikezeli wesazisi

data.name: CreateUsers.HelpText
data.value: Ngaba ufuna ukuba abasebenzisi abatsha badalwe ngokuzenzekelayo? Ukuba ukhubaza olu khetho, abasebenzisi kufuneka sele bhalisiwe kwisiza ukuze bangene ngemvume yabo yangaphandle.

data.name: DomainFilter.HelpText
data.value: Provide any email domain filter criteria (separated by commas). Domains to exclude should be prefixed with an exclamation point (!). For example 'microsoft.com,!hotmail.com' would include microsoft.com email addresses but not hotmail.com email addresses.

data.name: EmailClaimType.HelpText
data.value: Optionally specify the type name of the email address claim provided by the identity provider. The typical value is 'email'.

data.name: MetadataUrl.HelpText
data.value: Isiphelo sokufumanisa ukufumana imethadatha kulo mboneleli wesazisi. Cacisa kuphela ukuba umnikezeli wesazisi akasebenzisi indlela esemgangathweni (okt. /.well-known/openid-configuration)

data.name: PKCE.HelpText
data.value: Bonisa ukuba ngaba umnikezeli wesazisi uyasixhasa isitshixo sobungqina sokutshintshiselana ngekhowudi (PKCE)

data.name: ProviderName.HelpText
data.value: Cacisa igama elinobuhlobo lomnikezeli wokungena wangaphandle oya kubonakalisa kwiphepha lokungena

data.name: RedirectUrl.HelpText
data.value: I-URL yokuqondisa kwakhona (okanye i-url yokubuyisela umnxeba) ehlala ifuna ukubhaliswa kunye nomnikezeli wesazisi

data.name: Scopes.HelpText
data.value: Uluhlu lweendawo zokucela kumnikezeli wesazisi (ezahlulwe ngamakoma). Ukuba akukho nto ichaziweyo, imida esemgangathweni iya kusetyenziswa ngokungagqibekanga.

data.name: UserInfoUrl.HelpText
data.value: Isiphelo sokufumana ulwazi lomsebenzisi. Oku kufuneka kube sisiphelo se-API okanye i-url yephepha eliqulethe idilesi ye-imeyile yomsebenzisi.

data.name: CookieName.HelpText
data.value: Unokukhetha ukusebenzisa igama lekhukhi yokuqinisekiswa kwesiko kwiwebhusayithi nganye. Nangona kunjalo, nceda uqaphele ukuba ukuba ufuna ukwabelana nge-cookie yokuqinisekiswa phakathi kweesayithi kwi-domain efanayo, kufuneka basebenzise igama le-cookie elihambelanayo. Kwakhona qaphela ukuba ukutshintsha igama le-cookie yokuqinisekiswa kuya kukhupha bonke abasebenzisi abakhoyo.

data.name: Lifetime.HelpText
data.value: Inani lemizuzu apho umqondiso kufuneka usebenze

data.name: Secret.HelpText
data.value: Ukuba ufuna ukubonelela ngokufikelela kwi-API, nceda uchaze imfihlo eza kusetyenziswa ukufihla iithokheni zakho. Imfihlelo kufuneka ibe ngabalinganiswa abali-16 okanye ngaphezulu ukuqinisekisa ukhuseleko olufanelekileyo. Nceda uqaphele ukuba ukuba utshintsha le mfihlelo, zonke iithokheni ezikhoyo ziya kuba zingasebenzi kwaye kuya kufuneka zenziwe kwakhona.

data.name: Token.HelpText
data.value: Khetha i Yenza iqhosha lethokheni ukuvelisa ithokheni yofikelelo oluhlala ixesha elide (esebenzayo unyaka o-1). Qiniseka ukuba ugcina lo mqondiso kwindawo ekhuselekileyo njengoko awuyi kuba nakho ukufikelela kuyo kwixesha elizayo.

data.name: TwoFactor.HelpText
data.value: Ingaba ufuna abasebenzisi basebenzise ubungqina bezinto ezimbini? Qaphela ukuba ungasebenzisa ukhetho olukhubazekileyo de uqinisekise ngempumelelo ukuba Umsebenzi Wesaziso kwiMisebenzi Ecwangcisiweyo yenziwe kwaye iinketho zakho ze SMTP kwi Izicwangciso Zenxuwa ziqwalaselwe okanye kungenjalo uzakuzitshixa ngaphandle.

data.name: IdentifierClaimType.HelpText
data.value: Specify the type name of the unique user identifier claim provided by the identity provider. The default value is 'sub'.

data.name: Parameters.HelpText
data.value: Ngokuzikhethela, cacisa naziphi na iiparameter ezongezelelweyo njengegama / ixabiso leebhanki zokuthumela kumnikezeli wesazisi (ezahlulwe ziikoma ukuba kukho ezininzi).

data.name: RoleClaimType.HelpText
data.value: Optionally provide the type name of the roles claim provided by the identity provider (the standard default is 'roles'). If role names from the identity provider do not exactly match your site role names, please use the Role Claim Mappings.

data.name: RoleClaimMappings.HelpText
data.value: Optionally provide a comma delimited list of role names provided by the identity provider, as well as mappings to your site roles. For example if the identity provider includes an 'Admin' role name and you want it to map to the 'Administrators' site role you should specify 'Admin:Administrators'.

data.name: SynchronizeRoles.HelpText
data.value: Olu khetho luza kongeza okanye lususe izabelo zendima ukwenzela ukuba iindima zesiza zihambelane ngokuchanekileyo neendima ezinikezelwa ngumnikezeli wesazisi kumsebenzisi

data.name: ProfileClaimTypes.HelpText
data.value: Optionally provide a comma delimited list of user profile claim type names provided by the identity provider, as well as mappings to your user profile definition. For example if the identity provider includes a 'given_name' claim and you have a 'FirstName' user profile definition you should specify 'given_name:FirstName'.

data.name: AuthFlow.CodeIdTokenToken
data.value: Ikhowudi yogunyaziso + ithokheni ye-ID + ithokheni yokufikelela

data.name: AuthResponseType.HelpText
data.value: Cacisa uhlobo lwempendulo yogunyaziso. Ukungagqibeki yiKhowudi yoGunyaziso ethathwa njengeyona ndlela ikhuselekileyo ngokusekwe kwiinkcukacha zamva nje ze-OAuth.

data.name: VerifyUsers.HelpText
data.value: Ngaba ufuna abasebenzisi abakhoyo benze inyathelo elongezelelweyo lokuqinisekisa i-imeyile ukudibanisa ukungena kwabo kwangaphandle? Ukuba ukhubaza olu khetho, abasebenzisi abakhoyo bazakudityaniswa ngokuzenzekelayo.

data.name: AlwaysRemember.HelpText
data.value: Ukwenza olu khetho kuya kuseta i-cookie esisigxina ngokudibeneyo nexesha lokuphelelwa kwekhukhi, eliya kuthi lingene ngokuzenzekelayo kubasebenzisi kwixesha elizayo xa bendwendwela indawo. Ngokungagqibekanga, iwebhusayithi iya kusebenzisa ii-cookies zeseshoni.

data.name: CookieExpiration.HelpText
data.value: You can choose to use a custom authentication cookie expiration timespan for each site (e.g. '08:00:00' for 8 hours). The default is 14 days if not specified.

data.name: ReviewClaims.HelpText
data.value: Olu khetho luya kurekhoda uluhlu olupheleleyo lwamabango abuyiselwe ngumboneleli kwilog yesiganeko. Kufuneka isetyenziswe kuphela ngeenjongo zovavanyo. Ungeno lwangaphandle luya kuthintelwa xa olu khetho lusebenze.

data.name: NameClaimType.HelpText
data.value: Optionally specify the type name of the user's name claim provided by the identity provider. The typical value is 'name'.

data.name: SaveTokens.HelpText
data.value: Cacisa ukuba iimpawu zofikelelo nokuhlaziya zimelwe zigcinwe na emva kokungena ngempumelelo. Ukungagqibeki akuyonyani ukunciphisa ubungakanani becookie yokuqinisekisa.

data.name: LogoutEverywhere.HelpText
data.value: Ingaba ufuna ukuba abasebenzisi baphume kwiiseshoni nganye esebenzayo nakweyiphi na isixhobo, okanye kuphela iseshoni yabo yangoku?

data.name: AllowHostRole.HelpText
data.value: Bonisa ukuba iindima zomququzeleli zixhaswa ngumnikezeli wesazisi. Nceda uqaphele olu khetho njengoko luvumela umsebenzisi womninimzi ukuba alawule zonke iindawo ngaphakathi kofakelo lwakho.
